            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1232741</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>过往一级方程式赛车的 emoji，都是一架「红色的跑车」🏎。而 WhatsApp 决定为赛车 emoji 大翻新，新 emoji 将呈现 Mercedes-AMG PETRONAS F1 团队的颜色。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232586" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/1714459543_whatsapp_-694x441.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="441" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/1714459543_whatsapp_-694x441.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/1714459543_whatsapp_.jpg 760w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>WhatsApp 今次同 Mercedes AMG PETRONAS F1 团队合作，新 WhatsApp 赛车表情符号现呈现黑色底，辅以青蓝色的点缀。新 emoji 日前在美国纽约帝国大厦亮相。此 emoji 将会陆续向全球 WhatsApp 用户推送。另外 Mercedes-AMG 也在 WhatsApp 建立品牌频道，提供各种资讯。</p><p>WhatsApp 自从被收购以来，Meta 一直努力维持 WhatsApp 的非广告化立场。虽然曾有关于 WhatsApp 将引入广告的报导，但负责人 Will Cathcart 已作出否认。Meta 通过为企业建立独立应用与功能，成功地从这款即时通讯应用中获利。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">we upgraded the race car emoji so you never forget we’re team <a href="https://twitter.com/MercedesAMGF1?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@mercedesamgf1</a> 🏆 <a href="https://t.co/jPI4F3BrhQ">pic.twitter.com/jPI4F3BrhQ</a></p><p>&mdash; WhatsApp (@WhatsApp) <a href="https://twitter.com/WhatsApp/status/1785066883433079173?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">April 29, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/27/whatsapp-beta-dialler-hidden-group/software/android-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">WhatsApp 开发电话拨号器，方便用户随时致电他人</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/26/whatsapp-ios-now-added-passkey-support/software/ios-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">WhatsApp 提升保安功能，宣布为 iOS 程式加入 Passkey 支援</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/25/whatsapp-keep-chats-organized-with-chat-filters/life-tech/social-network/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">WhatsApp 新增对话列表筛选条件，助用家快速找到所需讯息</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/01/whatsapp-mercedes-amg/life-tech/auto/">再见「红色的跑车」 WhatsApp 一级方程式 Emoji 用 Mercedes-AMG 赛车配色</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
