        <item>
            <title>中国「Sora 级」影片大模型 Vidu【有片睇】  制作具中国特色影片 + 文字转换成 16 秒 1080P 影片</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/01/vidu/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=vidu</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/01/vidu/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 07:00:30 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Vidu]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1232742</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>日前中国中关村人工智能论坛中，清华大学联合生数科技宣布推出 Vidu－－中国首个 Sora 级的影片制作人工智能模型，标志著中国国产自研人工智能在影片技术领域取得了重大突破。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232588" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/vidu138screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/vidu138screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/vidu138screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232592" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/vidu1142screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/vidu1142screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/vidu1142screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>该模型展示了其在时空一致性、多镜头生成能力方面的优势，能够根据文字描述，直接生成高达 1080P 解像度长达 16 秒的影片。</p><p>Vidu 采用了由清华大学联合生数科技团队自研的 U-ViT 架构，此架构融合了 Diffusion 技术与 Transformer 技术。生数科技首席科学家朱军教授指，这一架构能够支援影片内容的快速生成，并强调这是全球首个此类融合架构，完全由团队自主研发。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232591" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/vidu1141screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/vidu1141screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/vidu1141screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232589" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/vidu339screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/vidu339screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/vidu339screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Vidu 能够模拟真实物理世界，同时展示丰富的想象力，例如生成具有特定中国文化标志的影片，如熊猫、龙等。朱军指出，Vidu 的命名寓意著「Video」和「We do」，强调团队的创新和实际执行力。他还提到，自 Sora 发布以来，团队在影片长度和处理技术方面进一步突破，大幅提升影片的连贯性和动态性。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232590" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/vidu1040screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/vidu1040screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/vidu1040screenshot.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>朱军教授表示，Vidu 的推出是一个多维度、跨领域的综合成果，期待通过与产业链各方面的深入合作，共同推动影片制作大模型技术的进一步发展。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_95936"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Fk8Q8szu-pA?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.chinanews.com.cn/cj/2024/04-27/10207442.shtml">中国新闻网</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/01/vidu/ai/">中国「Sora 级」影片大模型 Vidu【有片睇】  制作具中国特色影片 + 文字转换成 16 秒 1080P 影片</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
